kserick2.bio: I am a first year student in Computer Science and Anthropology.  Growing up, I had the distinction of being the only generation to have grown up alongside the evolution of internet based communication systems (social media).  As such, I have always been fascinated by the impact these platforms have had on redefining the significance and means of interpersonal relationships.  With a degree in Computer Science and Anthropology, I hope to investigate the far reaching impact of social media on changing the fabric of social hierarchies in society across time.
kserick2.name: Kyle Erickson
